title.newValue: Visio: EPC, Fault Tree Analysis, Audit, and Compliance stencils in Visio for the web [Visio Plan 1, Plan 2]

description.newValue:
Users with a Visio Plan 1 or Visio Plan 2 license will be able to create additional business diagrams from a blank drawing using four new Business stencils in Visio for the web.
GA date: September CY2022
